            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304813</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>HP 今日在香港发布一系列全新 Next Gen AI PC (Copilot+ PC)，主打结合人工智能技术与个人电脑的全新使用体验，产品阵容针对不同用家需求而设，包括适合自由工作者及流动用家的 OmniBook X Flip 14、OmniBook 7 Aero 13、OmniBook 5 16，以及为电竞爱好者打造的 OMEN MAX 16，更有一款适合家居及办公室使用的 HP 24 All-in-One Desktop，进一步扩展 AI PC 的应用层面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304830" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>HP OmniBook X Flip 14 — 灵活变形，自由工作者的 AI 拍档</h2><p>HP OmniBook X Flip 14 是一款专为多元工作场景而设的轻薄笔记型电脑，采用铝镁合金机身，兼具轻巧与坚固。其 360 度翻转设计，让用家随时转换笔记型电脑与平板电脑模式，无论是坐在咖啡店回复电邮，还是在家追剧，都能灵活应用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC05606" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54473054863/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54473054863_5afa4aa3a1_b.jpg" alt="DSC05606" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05611" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472786141/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472786141_77de2532aa_b.jpg" alt="DSC05611" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>处理效能方面，这款电脑可选用 Intel Core Ultra 7 或 AMD Ryzen AI 5 处理器，搭配专属 AI 引擎，最高达 50 NPU TOPS，支援 AI 图像处理与数据分析，轻松应对日常工作与创作需求。结合 Copilot+PC 的 AI 功能，用家可以透过虚拟助手搜寻资料、管理档案、强化系统效能，实现更高效率的数位工作模式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><p>显示方面，配备 14 吋 OLED 触控萤幕，支援高达 3K 解像度及可变刷新率，让影像画质细致流畅，无论观看影片还是绘图创作，都能享受视觉盛宴。配合内建的 500 万像素 AI 高清镜头，与 Poly Camera Pro 软件，让视讯会议保持最佳画面质素。重量仅 1.39kg，电池续航力最长可达 14.75 小时，真正实现全天候的流动办公。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304819" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304820" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><h2>HP OmniBook 7 Aero 13 — 极致轻盈，满足随行工作需求</h2><p>OmniBook 7 Aero 13 主打轻便与效能兼备，机身薄至 16.5mm，重量不到 1kg，专为经常出门在外的用家设计。外型简约时尚，冰川银色调搭配镁铝合金材质，带来高质感触感与坚固机身。</p><p><a title="DSC05670" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471945607/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471945607_7280960889_b.jpg" alt="DSC05670" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05645" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54473056428/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54473056428_282c7aac18_b.jpg" alt="DSC05645" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>搭载 AMD Ryzen AI 7 350 八核心处理器，具备独立 NPU，支援 50 TOPS AI 运算，能够提升多工处理效率，应对混合办公场景。配备 13 吋 2.5K IPS 防眩光萤幕，画面清晰细腻，超过 90% 屏占比，无论是文件编辑或简报展示，都能提供广阔的视野。</p><p>音效与视讯同样不容忽视，采用 Poly Studio 音讯技术，支援 DTS:X Ultra，提供沉浸式听觉体验；500 万像素 IR 镜头，搭配 Poly Camera Pro，让视讯会议保持专业。配合 Copilot+PC 及 AI 伴侣，协助用家轻松完成日常任务，提升生产力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>HP OMEN MAX 16 — 久违的 HP 高效能电竞手提电脑</h2><p>针对重度玩家与内容创作者，OMEN MAX 16 最高可配备 Intel Core Ultra 9 处理器、NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090 流动版显示卡与 64GB DDR5 记忆体，满足 AAA 游戏与高效能应用需求。搭载 2.5K OLED 萤幕，并支援 OMEN Gaming Hub 内的「释放模式」，可将 TPP 推至 250W，释放硬件潜能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC05666" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471945107/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471945107_1371554847_b.jpg" alt="DSC05666" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05663" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944997/in/album-72177720325418985/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944997_b7a37d3311_b.jpg" alt="DSC05663" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其创新的 OMEN Tempest Cooling Pro 冷却系统，结合液金属混合散热物料 OMEN Cryo Compound 与风扇自动清洁技术，让效能稳定发挥。机内使用液态金属散热技术，而为免物料在机内溢出，HP 采用特别混合物料 OMEN Cryo Compound，将液态金属结合矽胶，提升粘度，既提供优秀散热效果，又减低渗漏风险。此外新推 HP 与 Intel 协作的风扇自动清洁技术，会定期反转风扇转动方向，以防止灰尘积聚，确保性能表现之余，亦让玩家无需频繁清洁。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16-673x580.png" alt="" width="673" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16-673x580.png 673w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16.png 1044w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 673px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304822" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲用户可设定是否使用自动清理功能（自动清理功能会反向转动风扇，如用家长期打机，可关掉此功能）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304823" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304824" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304825" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>外观设计则配备 RGB 灯效，并支援个性化调校，为玩家打造独一无二的沉浸式体验。</p><p><a title="DSC05624" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944032/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944032_692c7e5bee_b.jpg" alt="DSC05624" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05628" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944162/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944162_d01a26ac5f_b.jpg" alt="DSC05628" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2></h2><h2>HP OmniBook 5 16 — 可靠耐用，兼顾工作与娱乐</h2><p>对于追求稳定效能和实用性的人士，OmniBook 5 16 是理想之选。搭载 AMD Ryzen AI 5 处理器，配备高达 50 TOPS AI 引擎，内建 16GB LPDDR5x 记忆体，兼具 AI 加速与多工效能，让日常工作更顺畅。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb-682x580.png" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb-682x580.png 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb.png 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a><a title="DSC05614" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472786221/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472786221_b5b6ab757a_b.jpg" alt="DSC05614" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05618" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472985069/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472985069_72fb711ecf_b.jpg" alt="DSC05618" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>采用 16 吋 2K WUXGA 触控萤幕，提供更大显示空间，轻松处理多个视窗或享受影音娱乐。铝金属机身配以天空蓝色调，提升质感。搭载 True Vision 1080p FHD IR 视讯镜头，支援私隐护盖，保障个人私隐。</p><h2>HP 24 All-in-One Desktop — 简洁一体，适合家居与办公</h2><p>HP 24 All-in-One Desktop 配备 AMD Ryzen 5 AI 340 处理器，为家居与办公环境提供高效、简洁的使用体验。一体化设计节省空间，萤幕与主机合而为一，适合会议、文书处理或多媒体娱乐。</p><h2>HP 全新系列电脑香港售价</h2><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top">产品</td><td valign="top">售价</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook X Flip 14</td><td valign="top">由 HK$10,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook 7 Aero 13</td><td valign="top">由 HK$8,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook 5 16</td><td valign="top">由 HK$7,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OMEN MAX 16</td><td valign="top">由 HK$22,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP 24 All-in-One Desktop PC</td><td valign="top">由 HK$8,999 起</td></tr></tbody></table><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/18_omenmax16-scaled.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/24/hp-copilot-plus-pc/notebook/">香港 HP 全新 Copilot+ PC 系列发布，同场加映：新 OMEN MAX 16 高效能电竞手提电脑</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
